<h1>Reset your password</h1>
<p>Hi {{name}},</p>
<p>We received a request to reset the password for your Stellar Creators account. Click the button below to choose a new password.</p>
<a href="{{resetUrl}}" class="btn">Reset Password</a>
<hr class="divider" />
<p class="small">This link expires in <strong>1 hour</strong>. If you didn't request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email — your password won't change.</p>
<p class="small">If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this URL into your browser:</p>
<p class="small">{{resetUrl}}</p>
